Interview Question
Q. Client aur Server Dry Run me difference?

Answer:

Client Dry Run sirf local machine par YAML aur command ki basic validation karta hai. API Server se connect nahi hota.
Server Dry Run request ko OpenShift API Server tak bhejta hai aur wahan schema validation, RBAC, namespace, admission controllers, quotas aur policies sab check karta hai, lekin resource actually create nahi karta.

